videos.headline: Brooks, Williams lead Oklahoma to Alamo Bowl win over Oregon
videos.description: Kennedy Brooks runs for three touchdowns while Caleb Williams throws for three as Oklahoma gets the 47-32 Alamo Bowl win over Oregon.
